      • equals

        public boolean equals(Object obj)

        Compares the specified object with this InterledgerAddress for equality.

        The InterledgerAddress interface is essentially a type-safe wrapper around a String value, so implementations should take care to forward equality decisions to the String.equals(Object) method on the object returned by InterledgerAddress.getValue().

        オーバーライド:
        equals クラス内 Object
        パラメータ:
        obj - object to be compared for equality with this collection
        戻り値:
        true if the specified object is equal to this InterledgerAddress.
        関連項目:
        Object.equals(Object), Set.equals(Object), List.equals(Object)
